{"seeAlsoSections":[{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The matching API reference for the views described here lives in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation."}],"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation"},{"title":"How-to Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"],"generated":true,"anchor":"How-to-Guides"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopresenttheui"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"How to Present the UI","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}]},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Attach "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallSheet"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterSheet"},{"type":"text","text":" from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" to a root view, driven by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" ships two SwiftUI views and a convenience modifier that wrap RevenueCatUI’s surfaces with platform-aware presentation. Each is bound to "},{"code":"PaywallState","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": presentation flags drive visibility, dismissal closures dispatch matching paywall actions back through the store. There is no local sheet state."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For platform behavior details (iOS "},{"code":"fullScreenCover","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" vs macOS sheet sizing, App Store deep link on macOS), see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Before you start","anchor":"Before-you-start"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide assumes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You have completed ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"text":". The plugin is registered and ","type":"text"},{"code":"observeCustomerInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" runs on launch.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app target depends on the ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" product:","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Step-1-Attach-both-sheets-to-a-root-view","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Step 1: Attach both sheets to a root view"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The simplest wiring uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall(state:send:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier — one call, both sheets, both dismissals:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","","struct RootView: View {","    @Environment(AppStore.self) private var store","","    var body: some View {","        ContentView()","            .revenueCatPaywall(state: store.paywall) { action in","                store.send(.paywall(action))","            }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The closure receives a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallAction"},{"type":"text","text":" ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismiss"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismissCustomerCenter"},{"text":") and lifts it into your root action. Place the modifier on the topmost view that should host both sheets.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Step 2: Trigger the paywall from a feature","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Step-2-Trigger-the-paywall-from-a-feature"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispatch "},{"code":".request(reason:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with a short identifier describing why you’re asking. "},{"code":"PaywallState.requestedReason","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" stores the value so the sheet (or analytics) can tailor its copy:"}]},{"code":["Button(\"Export PDF\") {","    store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"export-pdf\")))","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The plugin sets ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallState.isPresented = true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallSheet"},{"text":" observes the change and presents ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatUI.PaywallView"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Step-3-Trigger-the-customer-center","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Step 3: Trigger the customer center"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Existing subscribers manage their subscription through the customer center. Surface a button that dispatches ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".presentCustomerCenter"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["if store.paywall.isPro {","    Button(\"Manage Subscription\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.presentCustomerCenter))","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterSheet"},{"text":" presents ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatUI.CustomerCenterView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on iOS. On macOS it opens the system App Store subscriptions URL and immediately fires "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onDismiss"},{"text":" (RevenueCatUI does not ship a customer center on macOS — see ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"text":"Step 4: Manual wiring (optional)","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-4-Manual-wiring-optional","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need only one sheet, or you want to interleave other modifiers between them, attach each manually:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["ContentView()","    .background(","        PaywallSheet(","            isPresented: store.paywall.isPresented,","            onDismiss: { store.send(.paywall(.dismiss)) }","        )","    )","    .background(","        CustomerCenterSheet(","            isPresented: store.paywall.isCustomerCenterPresented,","            onDismiss: { store.send(.paywall(.dismissCustomerCenter)) }","        )","    )"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The modifier form is exactly equivalent to this wiring."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Step 5: Restore from inside the paywall","anchor":"Step-5-Restore-from-inside-the-paywall"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"RevenueCatUI’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" provides its own restore button by default. If you need an additional restore affordance elsewhere (a Settings row, for example), dispatch "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".restorePurchases"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["Button(\"Restore Purchases\") {","    store.send(.paywall(.restorePurchases))","}",".disabled(store.paywall.isLoading)"]},{"anchor":"What-happens-on-dismiss","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"What happens on dismiss"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the user dismisses the paywall, the plugin’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismiss"},{"type":"text","text":" action clears "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState.isPresented"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestedReason"},{"text":", then dispatches ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".refreshCustomerInfo"},{"text":" so the gate is reconciled — the user may have purchased while the sheet was open.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the user dismisses the customer center, the plugin’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dismissCustomerCenter"},{"text":" action clears ","type":"text"},{"code":"isCustomerCenterPresented","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". No refresh is dispatched, since opening the customer center does not change entitlement state by itself; the live "},{"code":"customerInfoStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" from "},{"code":"Step 5","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"type":"text","text":" picks up any subscription change RevenueCat reports asynchronously."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToAddAPermanentLicense":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","type":"topic","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Sell a lifetime entitlement alongside a subscription and surface both flags through the paywall plugin.","type":"text"}],"role":"article","title":"How to Add a Permanent License","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoaddapermanentlicense"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToImplementService":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Wire ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" into the ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" plugin so the store sees real-time entitlement updates from RevenueCat.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoimplementservice","role":"article","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","title":"How to Implement the Service"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"text":". Implements ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"text":" against ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" for drop-in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterView"},{"text":" presentation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","role":"collection","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/PlatformBehavior":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Why "},{"code":"PaywallSheet","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"CustomerCenterSheet","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" present differently on iOS and macOS, and what is hard-coded.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/platformbehavior","role":"article","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior","title":"Platform Behavior"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPreviewAndTest":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopreviewandtest","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Drive entitlement state from SwiftUI previews and tests with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" — no RevenueCat SDK call required."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest","role":"article","title":"How to Preview and Test"}}}